        array('id' => '17','post_id' => '8','key' => 'short_description','value' => 'Today we are announcing an update to the way payouts to sellers are handled at Prompt Market, which will come into effect starting Monday, June 26th, 2023.
            The two changes are the introduction of minimum payout amounts, and switching from daily payouts to weekly & monthly payout cycles.'),
        array('id' => '18','post_id' => '8','key' => 'main_description','value' => '<p>Over the past few months, we have received numerous requests to change our current payout system, and many sellers are on one of these new payout schedules already, however with this update everyone will move over.</p><p>We have decided to do this for a number of reasons:</p><ul><li>Stripe, our payment processor, charges a monthly fee per active account, and an additional fee for each payout. With daily payouts, these charges add up quickly. By switching away from many daily payouts of tiny amounts, we significantly reduce these costs.</li><li>For accounting purposes, and reporting income as a seller, it is difficult to tally up many small payouts, and much easier to work with weekly/monthly payouts.</li><li>Switching away from daily payouts helps us better prevent against scams &amp; fraud on our platform.</li></ul><p>As a new seller, you will start on a monthly payout schedule, and once you hit 50 sales, you will have the option to change over to weekly payouts if you wish.</p><p>For people who are currently collectors of digital art, they have a long view on how things will evolve. Understanding the ways that the work of this moment will grow and change as we move onward in time takes perspective. The story of art is a long one.</p><ul><li>Adjust the work/life balance.</li><li>Manage your workspace and organize your desk.</li><li>Keep In touch with your co-workers.</li><li>Get yourself comfortable.</li></ul>'),
        array('id' => '19','post_id' => '8','key' => 'seo','value' => '{"title":"Updates to Payout Cycles & Minimum Payouts","description":"Today we are announcing an update to the way payouts to sellers are handled at Prompt Market, which will come into effect starting Monday, June 26th, 2023.The two changes are the introduction of minimum payout amounts, and switching from daily payouts to weekly & monthly payout cycles.","tags":"prompt, market, payout"}'),
