        array('id' => '26','post_id' => '10','key' => 'main_description','value' => '<p>The title and description of the bundle will be displayed to potential buyers, in the same way a regular prompt\'s title and description is used.</p><p>The discount is applied to each individual prompt within the bundle.</p><p>The following restrictions apply to creating bundles:</p><ul><li>Titles can include no special characters</li><li>Titles are limited to 40 characters</li><li>Descriptions are limited to 200 characters</li><li>Discounts can be 5%, 10%, 15%, 20%, or 25%</li><li>Bundles must include at least 2 prompts</li><li>All prompts included in the bundle must be in an \'Approved\' state</li><li>A prompt can only be in one bundle at a time</li></ul><p>In addition to this, there are separate limits on the maximum number of prompts that can be included in a bundle. This is determined by your number of sales, and is viewable in your collections tab<a href="https://promptbase.com/account?view=perks">.</a></p><ul><li><strong>25 sales: </strong>Maximum of 2 prompts per bundle</li><li><strong>75 sales: </strong>Maximum of 3 prompts per bundle</li><li><strong>125 sales: </strong>Maximum of 4 prompts per bundle</li></ul>'),
